{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteam_Overview_.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One of your friends has been possessed by one of the 7 deadly Sins! Work as a team to identify and banish this deadly Sin hiding amongst you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with 5-15 players in the <strong>Multiplayer</strong> <u>OR</u> Play alone against crafty AI in the <strong>Single-player</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whilst investigating areas of paranormal activity trust and suspicion intertwine as those who remain Human attempt to unravel the identities of the disguised Sins before being taken out. Banish Sins from the game either in combat, or via collective vote.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring personal equipment to gather evidence cooperatively or alone to expose the Sins identity. Think you know who the Sin is? Gather around the evidence table to start a vote. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/Voting_Sincognito.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the essence of the Sins\u2019 souls lurking in areas around the map where it can be captured. Deposit the essence into a bubbling cauldron to weaken the Sins you believe are in play. Be sure to keep the fire alive as Sins will aim to extinguish the cauldrons fire before their essence is destroyed.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/Collect_Essense.gif?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteam_7DeadlySins_.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sins are able to transform between their disguised human form, and their true Sin identity. Once in their Sin form, each Sin has their own unique abilities that will facilitate different playstyles to combat the Humans and keep their Sin identity hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamPrideIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PRIDE</strong>: Traverses across the map using dimensional portals, forcing players to do its bidding.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamGreedsIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GREED:</strong> Sneakily stashes items found around the map into a bag to pack a bigger punch. Greed is also required to betray and kill all players - including fellow Sins - to win the game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamLustIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LUST:</strong> Pull unsuspecting Humans in and puppeteer their corpse to further deceive players.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamEnvyIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ENVY:</strong> Sneak up behind players through invisibility, or morph into another player's likeness to unsuspectingly strike players from behind.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamGluttonyIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GLUTTONY: </strong>Big and slow, Gluttony corners players and eats them whole in one, leaving no evidence of a body behind.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamWrathsIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WRATH: </strong>Small and fast to stay out of sight, Wrath can hack 'n' slash players, increasing in stats the more damage is dealt.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamSlothIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SLOTH: </strong>Limited in stamina, Sloth attacks in small bursts, taking hold and disposing of players.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Support our small indie studio - <strong>Wishlist now!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736030171","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/page.bg.jpg?t=1736030171","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736030171","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736030171","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"LAN PvP","id":47},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"LAN Co-op","id":48},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>PUBLIC PLAYTESTING</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Grab your friends and request access to the pre-alpha playtest build. Follow our Steam Community Page for updates on the next public playtest.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteam_Overview_.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One of your friends has been possessed by one of the 7 deadly Sins! Work as a team to identify and banish this deadly Sin hiding amongst you!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play with 5-15 players in the <strong>Multiplayer</strong> <u>OR</u> Play alone against crafty AI in the <strong>Single-player</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Whilst investigating areas of paranormal activity trust and suspicion intertwine as those who remain Human attempt to unravel the identities of the disguised Sins before being taken out. Banish Sins from the game either in combat, or via collective vote.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring personal equipment to gather evidence cooperatively or alone to expose the Sins identity. Think you know who the Sin is? Gather around the evidence table to start a vote. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/Voting_Sincognito.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find the essence of the Sins\u2019 souls lurking in areas around the map where it can be captured. Deposit the essence into a bubbling cauldron to weaken the Sins you believe are in play. Be sure to keep the fire alive as Sins will aim to extinguish the cauldrons fire before their essence is destroyed.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/Collect_Essense.gif?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteam_7DeadlySins_.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sins are able to transform between their disguised human form, and their true Sin identity. Once in their Sin form, each Sin has their own unique abilities that will facilitate different playstyles to combat the Humans and keep their Sin identity hidden.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamPrideIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PRIDE</strong>: Traverses across the map using dimensional portals, forcing players to do its bidding.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamGreedsIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GREED:</strong> Sneakily stashes items found around the map into a bag to pack a bigger punch. Greed is also required to betray and kill all players - including fellow Sins - to win the game.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamLustIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>LUST:</strong> Pull unsuspecting Humans in and puppeteer their corpse to further deceive players.      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamEnvyIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>ENVY:</strong> Sneak up behind players through invisibility, or morph into another player's likeness to unsuspectingly strike players from behind.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamGluttonyIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>GLUTTONY: </strong>Big and slow, Gluttony corners players and eats them whole in one, leaving no evidence of a body behind.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamWrathsIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>WRATH: </strong>Small and fast to stay out of sight, Wrath can hack 'n' slash players, increasing in stats the more damage is dealt.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/7DeadlySinsSteamSlothIMG.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>SLOTH: </strong>Limited in stamina, Sloth attacks in small bursts, taking hold and disposing of players.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/extras/SincognitoSteamSpacer.png?t=1736030171\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Support our small indie studio - <strong>Wishlist now!</strong></p>","developers":["Knockback Games"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2174060/header.jpg?t=1736030171","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recomm